Summary: I witnessed 3 UFOs within a 7-minute timeline, with remarkable aerodynamic ability.
divs: Sighting Detailson May 18th 2013 I witness the three objects in the sky, one object was moving westward slowly in between the clouds, the cloud coverage on that night was only approximately maybe 3000 feet. as the object moves through the clouds it illuminated the cloud each time it passed through one. the object look like some sort of the sphere glowing. approximately five minutes later 2 more objects we're headed east at a much greater speed making identical patters in the sky together.
